OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrump wins reprieve as     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjudge cuts fraud bond to   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F$175m                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A judge in New York has granted Donald 
OL,6, Trump's request to pause his $464m     
OL,7, (#365m) fraud judgement, giving him 10 
OL,8, days to put up a reduced sum of $175m. 
OL,10,FThe former president's legal team had  
OL,11,Fpreviously said he was unable to secure
OL,12,Fa bond from a private company for the  
OL,13,Ffull amount.                           
OL,15,FHe had faced a deadline of Monday to   
OL,16,Fpost the $464m bond.                   
OL,18,FIf he had failed to do, the authorities
OL,19,Fin New York could have started to seize
OL,20,Fhis bank accounts and properties.      
